ActNational Capital Act
SubjectLease with National Capital Business Protection Park Inc.** NCC **
PrecisOrder Approving that the National Capital Commission ENTER INTO A LEASE for an initial term of 49 years, and granting five extension options of ten years each, with NATIONAL CAPITAL BUSINESS PARK INC., to occupy the lands at 4055 and 4120 Russell Road, Ottawa, for the purpose of developing a new multi-tenant industrial site.
